       The Falling Sun is a horror game set in the under appreciated           
       location of late WW2 Burma. Keep your wits sharp as the environment     
       holds many surprises – and beware of what lurks in the dark. Take on    
       the role of a young British officer tasked with finding out the fate    
       of an armored division sent to put an end to the final remaining        
       pockets of Japanese resistance – as he begins to discover that the      
       situation is not as simple as it may at first appear. The game          
       currently ships with Act 1 with further free Acts on the way.           
                                                                               
                                                                               
